@node L16 "FAQ and problems"

                             FAQ and problems
                             ----------------


Q: The Game crashes during loading ! Why ?
A: It could be that the total RAM of your machine is not enough. Close
   all other programs, disconnect all external floppy drives and boot again,
   without startup-sequence.

Q: The graphics of the game are corrupted... why ?
A: The game DOES NEED a PAL-Screen to run properly ! Therefore you *MUST*
   use a Monitor capable of displaying PAL-Screens to run the game.
   If you are using a screen-promoter, advise it to re-route the game to a
   PAL-screen. In the Preferences-program "IControl" turn off the option
   "Same Mode".
   If this doesn`t work, try booting without startup-sequence.

Q: The screen turns to black during the menus.
A: Thats not really a problem, only your screensaver ;)


If you still have problems, try and reach me via eMail and tell me your
problems. I will give my best to help you.

@endnode





